                "invention-title": [
                    "Bi-component coated high-nickel positive electrode material and preparation method thereof",
                    "一种双组分包覆的高镍正极材料及其制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a double-component coated high-nickel positive electrode material and a preparation method thereof. The preparation method comprises the following steps: respectively dissolving a cobalt source, an aluminum source, ammonium hydrogen oxalate and a chelating precipitant by using ethanol as a solvent to obtain solutions A-D; adding a high-nickel positive electrode material and a dispersing agent into ethanol to obtain a mixed suspension E; adding the solution A into the mixed suspension E, dropwise adding the solution C in a stirring state for cobalt oxalate coating, filtering, drying and sintering to obtain a single-coated positive electrode material F; adding the solution B and the single-coated positive electrode material F into ethanol to obtain a suspension G, and dropwise adding the solution D to coat an aluminum component; and filtering, washing and drying the feed liquid, and carrying out high-temperature treatment in a nitrogen atmosphere. According to the method, the cycle performance of the high-nickel positive electrode material is remarkably improved, meanwhile, the whole coating process is carried out in an organic solution system, and the problem that the cycle of the high-nickel positive electrode material is deteriorated due to the fact that the chemical environment on the surface of the high-nickel positive electrode material is changed under the conventional water system condition is solved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种双组分包覆的高镍正极材料及其制备方法。所述制备方法包括如下步骤：以乙醇为溶剂分别溶解钴源、铝源、草酸氢铵和螯合沉淀剂得到溶液A‑D；将高镍正极材料和分散剂加入至乙醇中，得到混合悬浮液E；将溶液A加入到混合悬浮液E中，在搅拌状态下滴加溶液C进行草酸钴包覆，过滤、干燥、烧结得到单包覆正极材料F；将溶液B、单包覆正极材料F加入乙醇中得到悬浮液G，滴加溶液D进行铝组分的包覆；料液经过滤、洗涤和干燥后，在氮气气氛中进行高温处理即得。本发明显著提升了高镍正极材料的循环性能，同时整个包覆过程在有机溶液体系中进行，避免了在常规水系条件下水使高镍正极材料表面化学环境发生变化导致高镍正极材料循环恶化的问题。"
                }
            ]
